QuestData.Title: Checking Up
QuestData.Description: These marshes are beautiful, wouldn't you agree? That is, except for the naga forces draining the water away.$B$BI sent a small expedition to the Coilfang Reservoir to investigate the naga, and they haven't returned. I'm concerned that something has happened to them.$B$BWould you travel to the Slave Pens underneath Serpent Lake and find Watcher Jhang?
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak with Watcher Jhang in the Slave Pens.
